===Etymology===
From ''[[Marchantia]]'' (a genus of liverwort) + [[-phyta]]

===Proper noun===
'''Marchantiophyta'''

#{{botany}}: A [[botanical name]] for a [[taxon]] within [[kingdom]] [[Plantae]] that includes the [[liverwort]]s. The taxon is traditionally given the [[rank]] of a [[division]].

